long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
This is TurboPlacer, the Chrome extension that helps you maximize your YouTube revenue by automatically placing ads on your YouTube videos. Start your no credit card required 14 day trial today!

Say goodbye to the tedious and time-consuming process of manually placing ads on your content. With TurboPlacer, you can effortlessly place ads and maximize your revenue potential with just a few clicks.

Here's what TurboPlacer offers:

Seamless Integration
TurboPlacer seamlessly integrates with YouTube Studio, providing a smooth and intuitive workflow. Simply go to place ads on a video and the turbo place button will pop up! 

Customizable Settings
Take control of your ad placement preferences with TurboPlacer's flexible time placement settings.

You can choose to place ads every amount of seconds, minutes, or hours. Or if you simply want to place a certain amount of ads you can and it'll automatically space them out.

Increased Revenue Potential
Just because you place an ad doesn't mean YouTube will show it. By optimizing your ad placements, it can help ensure ads are shown to your audience.

Easy Setup and User-Friendly Interface
Getting started with TurboPlacer is a breeze. Simply install the Chrome extension, go to place ads and either sign up for a no credit card trial or buy for $9.99. Click the link in your email and refresh, and TurboPlacer is ready to run. 

Why Choose TurboPlacer?
Whether you're a seasoned YouTube creator or just starting your monetization journey, TurboPlacer is the ultimate tool to streamline your ad placement process.

Don't waste any more time manually placing ads on your videos. Let TurboPlacer do the heavy lifting for you, so you can focus on creating amazing content and engaging with your audience!
